blogs.title: EFO AND IYAN
blogs.author: Remi
blogs.content: This impressive Efo(Vegetable soup) and Iyan(Pounded Yam) are a perfect special occasional dish and a very nutritious one at that to make for your guests. 3 Bunches of your favourite Efo will likely do, if you like....
